title: Business To Generate NFTs From Decentraland
body:
> by 0x83cfa5852e10e746afb86c2544e419d96b016634 (marcuselola#6634)

Should the following Tier 3: up to a 3 month vesting contract of $3000 - $5000 USD in MANA, with a one month cliff grant in the Content Creator category be approved?

## Abstract

We Are A Small Startup Called CyberSeedZ Local To The Silicon Valley & Develop Professional Quality NFT Collectibles For Businesses / Individuals.

We Have  A Team Of Developers Working On Instantaneous NFT Contract Fulfillment In Decentraland, However We Currently Provide A 24hr Turnaround Time For Content Submissions.

Our Decentraland Shop Is  Coming Soon!!!

We Also Offer Services Generating Wearables & Building Decentraland Stores For Existing Businesses!

Feel Free To Check Us Out At CyberSeedZ.com & Have A Blessed Day!


## Grant size

5,000 MANA

## Beneficiary address

0x83CfA5852e10E746Afb86C2544E419d96b016634

## Description

Our Company Will Allow Its Users To Interact With Decentraland In A Way That Allows Them To Generate & Mint NFTs In-Game.


## Specification

Our Team Is Developing In The Solidity Coding Language To Determine The Most Efficient Method Of Developing Ethereum Blockchain NFTs From Our Planned Decentraland Storefront.


## Personnel

We Have A Charismatic Team Including 3D Asset Developers, Photographers, Media Producers, Graphic Designers, Coding Engineers, & Investors.


## Roadmap and milestones

We Plan To See Our First NFT Collection Release "Runtz Coinz" By California Fresh Products At A Non Disclosable Time Due To Contractual Agreement. This Release Will Be Taking Place Alongside A Physical Asset Add On Service Which Links Physical Objects To An ETH Wallet.

Thereafter, We Will Be Making A Further Internal Investment Toward The Development Of These Physical Assets.

In The Intermediate, Our Team Is Developing A Method Of Creating  ETH Based NFT Contracts  Inside Of Decentraland!

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/en/proposal/?id=6e3408a0-d38f-11eb-976f-4b50abb26a02)**
